Package fluent.ly

Enum box

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<box>
      • fluent.ly.box
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<box>
    public enum box
extends java.lang.Enum<box>
    A utility class, with a collection of function to box primitive types in their reference type equivalent representation. Similarly, this class offers functions to box arrays of primitive types into their reference type equivalent.
    Since:
    21/06/2008
    Author:
    Yossi Gil, the Technion.
    See Also:
    unbox
